## Question 6: Explain how business rules help in validating data accuracy. Give an example.

Business rules define conditions data must satisfy.

They help by:
- Ensuring logical consistency.
- Preventing invalid entries.
- Enforcing domain constraints.

Examples from dataset:
- Quantity should not be Null (Row 205 violates).
- Txn_Amount should not be Null (Row 206 violates).
- Txn_Date should not be Null (Row 207 violates).
- Customer_Name should not be "N/A".

